mil.nga.giat.geowave.store

Interface DeleteCallback<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - A generic type for ingested entries
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CountDataStatistics, DataStatisticsBuilder

    public interface DeleteCallback<T>
    This interface provides a callback mechanism when ingesting a collection of entries to receive the row IDs where each entry is ingested

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void entryDeleted(IngestEntryInfo entryInfo, T entry)
      This will be called after an entry is successfully ingested with the row IDs that were used
